trans-unit.source: Represents a WSDL violation of the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles"></xref> object that specifies whether the Web service declares that it conforms to the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles"></xref> object that specifies whether the Web service declares that it conforms to the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
Gets a <xref href="System.String"></xref> that provides a detailed description of the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile.
A <xref href="System.String"></xref> that provides a detailed description of the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile.
Represents WSDL elements that do not comply with the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"></xref> that contains the WSDL elements that do not comply with the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
Gets the identifier for the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
A <xref href="System.String"></xref> that contains the identifier (For example, R2038) for the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
Gets a <xref href="System.String"></xref> object that describes the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
The <xref href="System.String"></xref> object that describes the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.

Returns a <xref href="System.String"></xref> that comprises information from <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.NormativeStatement"></xref>, <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Details"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Elements"></xref>.

A <xref href="System.String"></xref> that comprises information from <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.NormativeStatement"></xref>, <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Details"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Elements"></xref>.
